== Stages ==

The 2015 event had a very similar format to the previous year's race.<ref name=cyclingnews-preview/> It consisted of six stages, of which five were flat stages and one was an [[individual time trial]].<ref name=pcs-stages>{{cite web|url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/race/Tour_of_Qatar_2015-stages|title=Tour of Qatar 2015 stages|website=ProCyclingStats|accessdate=6 February 2015}}</ref> The individual time trial, on the third day of racing, used precisely the same course as the corresponding stage in 2014.<ref>For the 2014 stage, see {{cite web|url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/race/Tour_of_Qatar_2014_Stage_3_Lusail-profiles|title=Tour of Qatar 2014 - Stage 3 (ITT)|website=ProCyclingStats|accessdate=5 April 2015}}
* For the 2015 stage, see {{cite web|url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/race/Tour_of_Qatar_2015_Stage_3_Lusail-profiles|title=Tour of Qatar 2015 - Stage 3 (ITT)|website=ProCyclingStats|accessdate=5 April 2015}}</ref>

